da-Suite-28thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>119</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2734</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>ExternalViewOfTheHotel</PhotoType></Photo><Photo><Url>/RXLImages/1116/26/37/2631759-Melia-Sierra-Nevada-Guest-Room-31.jpg</Url><Width>480</Width><Height>279</Height><Bytes>21754</Bytes><Caption>2631759-Melia-Sierra-Nevada-Guest-Room-31</Caption><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1116/26/37/2631759-Melia-Sierra-Nevada-Guest-Room-31thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>120</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2637</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>ViewOfAGuestRoom</PhotoType></Photo><Photo><Url>/RXLImages/1116/26/37/2631759-Melia-Sierra-Nevada-Meeting-Room-15.jpg</Url><Width>480</Width><Height>281</Height><Bytes>29097</Bytes><Caption>2631759-Melia-Sierra-Nevada-Meeting-Room-15</Caption><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1116/26/37/2631759-Melia-Sierra-Nevada-Meeting-Room-15thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>119</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2959</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>ViewOfAGuestRoom</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>Welcome to the Melia Sierra Nevada Hotel. The hotel provides the comfort and superior quality services expected of Melia hotels, and is set in an area providing all of the shopping and leisure facilities in the Sierra Nevada, just a few meters from the ski slopes, only 33 Km. from the historical monumental city of Granada and 43 Km. from the airport. A hotel with its own particular personality and a privileged location, where guests may enjoy the most highly personalized service and a wide range of facilities and services for both adults and children, including a great range of dining options including a full Buffet Restaurant, the cosy a la carte restaurant "La Tinaja de la Sierra", or the popular "La Bodeguita" Tapas bar. And all guaranteed by "Q" for Quality Certification. Allow yourself to be seduced by the charms of the Hotel Melia Sierra Nevada, a hotel with a passion for service, ideal for skiing, relaxation, business or as a base for exploring Granada, one of the most important cultural cities in Europe. 

The Melia Sierra Nevada is located in the heart of the Sierra Nevada ski resort at the bottom of the slopes. With warm and welcoming traditional mountain-style decoration where natural woods, stone, floor tiles and warming colours predominate all over, the Melia Sierra Nevada is the leading hotel in the resort thanks to an ability to evolve and adapt to the needs of the most demanding and discerning guests, without losing any of the traditional and noble charm which makes it a unique hotel, perfectly combining the mountain style with luxury and the greatest attention to the tiniest of details.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>Built in 1975, the Melia Sierra Nevada was the first 4 star hotel to open in the Sierra Nevada mountains, making it forever the leading hotel in the ski resort. Over many years, this emblematic hotel has been chosen by countless figures and personalities from the worlds of politics, the movies, music or sport for a winter break in the snow, and the Guest Book is full of illustrious names including the King and Queen of Spain, King Gustav and Queen Silvia of Sweden, the bullfighter Francisco Rivera Ordonez, the journalist Luis del Olmo, the singer Carlos Baute, the Aga Khan, and the racing driver Fernando Alonso, amongst many, many others.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>RoomTypes</Type><Text>Classic - Room - Comfortable, bright and welcoming rooms, decorated in traditional mountain style, in wood and warm tones. An ideal place to rest and relaxation after a hard day on the slopes or at work. The standard Classic - Room has a foldaway single bed while the standard quadruple rooms have a foldaway double bed (both subject to availability). They also provide a free baby cot when occupied by two people (on request). Services Room service from 8 am to 11 pm. (with extra charge) 24-hour Serviexpress customer service Laundry and ironing service (with extra charge) 24-hour wake-up call service Real time information on ski slopes through the TV Equipment 2 single beds or 1 double bed (subject to availability) Heating LCD satellite TV with Canal and theme channels Wi-Fi Internet access Telephone in the bedroom and bathroom Mini-Bar Free safe Desk Full length mirror Bathtub Hairdryer Make-up mirror Bathroom amenities Rooms available for non-smokers (on request).

Superior - Room - Superior Rooms at the Melia Sierra Nevada use natural wood and warm colors to bring warmth and comfort to the room, while the balcony provides light and exceptional views, making the rooms an ideal place for rest and relaxation. Superior Room offers two twin beds and one twin bed additional. They also provide a free baby cot when occupied by two people (on request). Services Room service from 8 am to 11 pm. (with extra charge) 24-hour Serviexpress customer service Laundry and ironing service (with extra charge) 24-hour wake-up call service Real time information on ski slopes through the TV. Equipment 2 single beds or 1 double bed (subject to availability) Heating LCD satellite TV with Canal and theme channels Wi-Fi Internet access Telephone in the bedroom and bathroom Minibar Free safe Desk Full length mirror Bathtub Hairdryer Make-up mirror Superior quality bathroom amenities Rooms available for non-smokers (on request).

Family - Room - Comfortable, bright and welcoming rooms, decorated in traditional mountain style, in wood and warm tones. An ideal place to rest and relaxation after a hard day on the slopes or at work. Family - Room offers three twin beds and one sofa bed. They also provide a free baby cot when occupied by two people (on request). Services Room service from 8 am to 11 pm. (with extra charge) 24-hour Serviexpress customer service Laundry and ironing service (with extra charge) 24-hour wake-up call service Real time information on ski slopes through the TV Equipment 2 single beds or 1 double bed (subject to availability) Heating LCD satellite TV with Canal and theme channels Wi-Fi Internet access Telephone in the bedroom and bathroom Mini-Bar Free safe Desk Full length mirror Bathtub Hairdryer Make-up mirror Bathroom amenities Rooms available for non-smokers (on request).</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MiniBarInRoom</Code><Text>Mini-bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RoomService</Code><Text>Room service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MoneyExchange</Code><Text>Money exchange</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Hairdresser</Code><Text>Hairdresser</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Bar</Code><Text>Bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>PublicInternetAccess</Code><Text>Public internet access</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>LaundryService</Code><Text>Laundry service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>CarPark</Code><Text>Car parking</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ReceptionArea</Code><Text>Reception Area</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Lift</Code><Text>Lift</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>ConferenceRoom</Code><Text>Conference Room</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>WLANAccessPoint</Code><Text>WLAN Access Point</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HeatedPool</Code><Text>Heated Pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Cod